</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Wolfe.</SPEAKER>
<L>Madam. I do &mdash;</L>
<L>Our <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">g<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> and patriot Mini&s;ter on me</L>
<L>Has h<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">'d his choice, to &s;tand prime candidate</L>
<L><GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">or ho<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">our in th<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">s glorious enterprize;</L>
<L>Our martial King (well pleas'd) gave his royal</L>
<L>A&s;&s;en<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> to that choice, and glory calls me forth.</L>
</SP>
<SP>
