<L>Reflected <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">o<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ou<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> on you their former</L>
<L>Chief? And Loui&s;bourg bore dreadful witne&s;s,</L>
<L>To y<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">u impetu<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">us and u<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">hated</L>
<L>Fur<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> in the &s;iege: Why then &s;hou'd future</L>
<L>Fame engro&s;s th' a<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">ention <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">f your &s;oul?</L>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Wolfe.</SPEAKER>
<L>Tho&s;e troops you're pleas'd to hint at; wh<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters"> they tought,</L>
<L>Were headed b<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> another: B<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">&s;ides, it</L>
<L>Is too scant an honour to &s;hine by their</L>
<L><PB N="8" REF="012729_0007_0F8BEB7609DE7188">Reflection, and borrow glory from tho&s;e</L>
<L>Gallant &s;<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ldiers deeds.&mdash;</L>
<L>At Loui&s;bourg, I wa<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> not fir&s;t in the</L>
<L>Command, and cannot claim the foremo&s;t rank</L>
<L>Of fame: Then I only took a gentle</L>
<L>Sip of honour's cup, but was with held by</L>
<L>De&s;tiny from draining it, which like true</L>
<L>Lovers ki&s;&s;es&punc; (&s;till rai&s;ing new de&s;ires,)</L>
<L>Has &s;et my thir&s;ty &s;oul in flame for more!</L>
