<L>Forgiv<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">, my &s;on, a mother's fears:</L>
<L>I wou'd not check you in your full career</L>
<L>To glory, nor from my country's &s;ervice</L>
<L>Willingly detain a brave and u&s;eful leader:&mdash;</L>
<L>My heart di&s;tends with &s;ecret pride, and joy</L>
