<L>Of danger, like him, &s;hri<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">k back into my</L>
<L>Shell? No!&mdash;let the&s;e re&s;emblances of men,</L>
<L>Who out&s;ide wear the martial garb, and &s;eem</L>
<L><PB N="9" REF="012729_0008_0F8BEB7741EADC28">To look the lio<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> in their &s;<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">l<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> po<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">t.</L>
