<SP>
<SPEAKER>Cal Ch.</SPEAKER>
<L>If Sir Jeffery Amer&s;t cannot join</L>
<L>Us with tho&s;e gallant troops he leads (which we</L>
<L>Indeed cou'd wi&s;h) let us not wa&s;te the &s;hort</L>
<L>L<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">'d &s;ea&s;on in fruitle&s;s wi&s;hes, and a</L>
<L>Di&s;tant war, or grieve becau&s;e the French by</L>
<L>U<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> are not out-number'<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">; but let us, as</L>
