<L>Sight invert their walls; no doubt' will <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">o<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ze the</L>
<L>Frenchm<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">n to a battle; and when the<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> &s;hall</L>
<L>Advance to fight, we w<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">l upon our&s;elves</L>
<L>R<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter">ly; and in our front &s;hall march &s;tern fate!</L>
<L>So&s;tain'd on either wing by gloomy terror!</L>
