</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Britann.</SPEAKER>
<L><GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> Gen'ral Amher&s;t join us not, yet he</L>
<L>Will be of &s;ervice to us, &s;hou'd w<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> be</L>
<L>Still compell'd to carry on the Siege by</L>
<L><PB N="53" REF="012729_0052_0F8BEBB5D561D8B0"><GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 span">: He keeps in awe the inland</L>
<L>I <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 word"> around, and is a crub on each &s;ort,</L>
