</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Britannicus.</SPEAKER>
<L>And on my &s;word <STAGE>[drawing his &s;word]</STAGE></L>
<L>I &s;wear <STAGE>[ki&s;&s;ing it]</STAGE>
with heart re&s;olv'd,</L>
<L>And re&s;olution firm to &s;truggle for</L>
<L>The palm of victory, and if we fail,</L>
<L>I'll not think life worth care, to &s;ave it by</L>
<L>A forc'd retreat.</L>
</SP>
<SP>
<SPEAKER>Fir&s;t Caledonian Chief,</SPEAKER>
<STAGE>[drawing his &s;word.]</STAGE>
<L>By this good <GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="2 letters">ade I &s;wear <STAGE><HI>[ki&s;&s;ing hi<GAP DESC="illegible" RESP="pdcc" EXTENT="1 letter"> &s;word]</HI></STAGE>
which never prov'd</L>
<L>Unfaithful to my arm, nor fail'd me in</L>
<L><PB N="55" REF="012729_0054_0F8BEBB758969DE0">The greate&s;t need; I'll put it once more to</L>
<L>The noble&s;t te&s;t, and thro' the thicke&s;t ranks</L>
